    weisTip:
      '<strong>House rules when opening a table:</strong> <em>“Weis only with a trick”</em> — anyone who takes no trick the whole round loses their Weis points again. <em>“Sack (min. 21)”</em> — anyone below 21 card points is “in the sack”: round and Weis points are forfeited entirely.',
